wikipedia_page.main: Nicholas Michael Murphy (born 25 December 1946) is an English former professional footballer who played in the Football League as a midfielder. He is the son of Manchester United former coach and temporary manager Jimmy Murphy.

response: Nicholas or Nick Murphy may also refer to:
*Nick Murphy (director), British film director and television director
*Chet Faker (born Nicholas James Murphy, 1988), Australian musician also known as Nick Murphy
